{"tid":1443353,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論]點解今日北角特別重兵？","createTime":"2019-08-11T07:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:55:10.000Z","uid":51555,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7357cd1a571a511b0bcb5ce67f18a50d724b5e27","tid":1443353,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:58:36.000Z","msg":"早前幾次即使有情報將有恐襲遊行嘅時候，啲狗一直零人手<br />\n目的就係比黑勢力打人<br />\n但係今次反常係沿途住重兵於當眼位置<br />\n有鑑於近日換新二哥上場， 目的想重新塑造狗隊形象<br />\n我有啲懷疑係狗隊想同黑勢力於<span style=\"color: red;\">朝早前後腳出現激起民憤</span><br />\n之後入黑後公佈狗收隊，咁一定有唔少睇唔過嘅勇武想去報復<br />\n咁到時狗隊就可以大大聲對外講日頭有狗嘅時候好安全<br />\n話係有黑衣人搞事先會亂， 同時可以build up形象又可以打我地手足"},{"pid":"52f9938b24b7ed8da0842cf42ef093f11bbff071","tid":1443353,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:17:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月11日</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">：「和你飛」&bull;入機場（1300）</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月11日</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月11日</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span>"},{"pid":"3d9020ff12781cdda5ef824ef940f37f6d5d6578","tid":1443353,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:27:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea7483d7f00dd7d6962c6b2223bb377f32e26609","tid":1443353,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"推 依家個個都唔遮樣 扮nice<br />\n想build up形象呀屌<br />\n行動組唔推 冷房軍師呢？"},{"pid":"ac0941e6aecc7e4868948725af2bbd20354e5992","tid":1443353,"uid":51555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-